Teriyaki Glazed Salmon with Asparagus

25 min
$12.5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

FishSoy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh ProteinLow Carb

Cuisine:

JapaneseAmerican

Course:

Main CourseDinner

Tags:

EasyQuickHealthyDinner

Description

A deliciously simple dish featuring tender salmon glazed in a sweet teriyaki sauce, paired with crisp asparagus for a healthy, flavorful meal.

Ingredients

  • salmon fillets: 2 (6 oz each)
  • teriyaki sauce: 1/4 cup
  • asparagus: 1 bunch
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
